Instructions for build

Prepare conan repos
$
conan remote add conan-center "https://conan.bintray.com"

git clone https://github.com/darcamo/conan-cxxopts
cd conan-cxxopts && conan create . local/stable
cd .. && rm -rf conan-cxxopts

pip install common --user
git clone https://github.com/msaf1980/conan-orocos-log4cpp
cd conan-orocos-log4cpp && conan create . local/stable
cd .. && rm -rf conan-orocos-log4cpp

Build
$
mkdir target
conan install ..
cmake ..
cmake --build .
